    <page type="text">
        <text>
A good tinkerer should know that the world is a dangerous and evil place with many things wishing to kill you. While tools and weapons are important, a good set of armor is vital to a tinkers continuous survival.
</text>
    </page>

    <page type="tailorSection">
        <section>Simple Armor Crafting</section>
        <text>Simple non-metal armor is a tinkerers first starting point for protection. These simple armor pieces are created in the part builder using the appropriate wooden patterns. However, this can only be done using simple non-metal materials, or relatively soft metals, such as iron and copper.</text>
    </page>

