    <page type="tailorSection">
        <section>Advanced Armor Crafting</section>
        <text>Armor made from even moderately hard metals cannot be made in the part builder. You must use a smeltery in order to melt down the metals into a molten liquid form (see Mighty Smelting). The molten metal can then be cast into an armor using the appropriate block cast.</text>
    </page>

